WEBVTT

00:00:13.331 --> 00:00:16.252 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
노아는 하느님과

00:00:16.252 --> 00:00:19.883 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
항상 함께 걸었죠.

00:00:20.634 --> 00:00:24.139 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
늘 가족과 마음 다해

00:00:24.139 --> 00:00:27.394 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
옳은 일을 했어요.

00:00:28.103 --> 00:00:31.358 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
커다란 그 방주도

00:00:31.358 --> 00:00:34.654 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
충실히 만들고

00:00:35.071 --> 00:00:38.117 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
여호와의 말씀을

00:00:38.117 --> 00:00:42.248 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
모두에게 전했죠.

00:00:42.228 --> 00:00:47.798 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
노아, 참 충실했던 노아,

00:00:47.777 --> 00:00:51.387 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
홍수 다가올수록

00:00:51.366 --> 00:00:55.316 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
힘껏 전파했죠.

00:00:57.020 --> 00:01:02.319 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
나도 충실한 노아처럼

00:01:02.299 --> 00:01:05.908 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
하느님과 걷는

00:01:05.887 --> 00:01:09.705 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
친구될래요.

00:01:13.335 --> 00:01:16.173 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
