00:01:16.173 --> 00:01:19.803 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
비웃고 위협해도

00:01:20.492 --> 00:01:24.122 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
노아는 가족 모두를

00:01:24.143 --> 00:01:27.690 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
끝까지 지켰죠.

00:01:27.669 --> 00:01:31.549 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
악하고 폭력 가득한

00:01:31.570 --> 00:01:34.908 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
그 세상 속에서

00:01:34.888 --> 00:01:38.518 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
기쁨을 잃지 않고

00:01:38.539 --> 00:01:42.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
끝까지 인내했죠.

00:01:42.273 --> 00:01:47.761 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
